Overview: As his wife is going to Thailand with her friends, Tin and his friends Cheung, Chao and Paul decide to seize the opportunity and taste 14 hours of freedom by putting their work aside and betraying their spouses. 
Besotted by the excitement and happiness, they follow their plans and enjoy every moment of freedom. Unfortunately, their spouses suddenly come back and decide to raid this betrayal action in secret. &lt;P&gt;

Problems and accidents happen during the plan is in process. They believe that someone in the dark comes and destroys their plan on purpose. Suspicion even starts growing among them, which they think that one of them must be the betrayer. However, what they do not know is that a limousine has been following them all along... &lt;P&gt;

